<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Organic Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css"> <!-- Link to your external stylesheet -->
    <style>
        /* Basic styles for About Us page */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        header {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .about-container h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .about-container p {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .about-container img {
            display: block;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include("../../views/partials/user/header") %>
        
    </header>

    <div class="about-container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
            At <strong>Organic Store</strong>, we believe in the power of nature to provide the purest, healthiest, and most sustainable products. 
            Founded with a mission to bring the best organic goods to your doorstep, we work directly with local farmers and trusted suppliers 
            to ensure every item meets our rigorous quality standards.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our store offers a wide range of organic fruits, vegetables, dairy, and pantry staples. 
            Everything we sell is free from harmful chemicals, synthetic fertilizers, and GMOs, so you can shop with confidence for your family.
        </p>
        <img src="/images/organic-store-white-logo.png" alt="Organic Farm" />
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            We are committed to promoting health, sustainability, and community. By choosing organic, you’re not only caring for your well-being 
            but also supporting eco-friendly practices and fair-trade principles.
        </p>
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Fresh, locally sourced organic products</li>
            <li>Eco-friendly packaging</li>
            <li>Dedicated to quality and sustainability</li>
            <li>Exceptional customer service</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            Thank you for choosing <strong>Organic Store</strong>. Together, let’s make healthier choices and nurture the planet for future generations.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
<%- include("../../views/partials/user/footer") %>
